ppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"currentVersionReleaseDate":"2026-03-17T06:10:57Z","version":"5.9.15","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"1881 Who’s Calling – formerly 1881 Mobilsøk\nGood news! The app has a new name – and a major upgrade.\nYou can now see who’s calling in real time, directly on your screen.\n\nWith 1881 Who’s Calling, you get automatic caller identification on all numbers listed in Opplysningen 1881 – Norway’s most trusted directory service.\n\nThis feature is now finally available on iPhone, giving you full control over who’s trying to reach you.\nWhether it’s a client, a courier, or an important message from daycare, 1881 helps you know who’s calling before you pick up.\n\n1881 Who’s Calling subscription\nThis app requires an active 1881 Mobilsøk or 1881 Who’s Calling subscription.\nIf you don’t already have one, you’ll be offered an in-app purchase at startup.\nNew customers receive a 30-day free trial, and you may cancel at any time.\n\nWith 1881 Who’s Calling, you get:\n•\tSee who’s calling – in real time (now on iPhone!)\n•\tCaller ID on all numbers – not just spam or sales calls\n•\tImproved protection against unwanted calls\n•\tUpdated name: 1881 Mobilsøk is now 1881 Who’s Calling\n\nBenefits of 1881 Who’s Calling:\n•\tKnow who’s calling before you answer\n•\tNever miss important calls\n•\tAvoid unwanted calls and fraud attempts\n•\tUnlimited searches in Opplysningen 1881 – without disruptive ads\n•\tUpdate and clean up your contacts with verified information\n•\tLook up missed calls instantly\n\nHow to activate “Who’s Calling”\n1. Open Settings\n2. Select Phone\n3. Choose Call Blocking & Identification\n4. Enable 1881 Who’s Calling\n\nSearch with 1881\nSearch for names, numbers, addresses, businesses, and categories directly in the app.\nYou can also search for nearby businesses like restaurants, pharmacies, gas stations, and more.\n\nUpdate your contacts\nEasily save or update contacts with accurate information from Opplysningen 1881.\nThe app gives you a clear overview of your contacts and shortcuts to call, text, or email.\n\nGroup SMS and conference calls no longer available\nThese features have been removed due to low usage.\n\nPrivacy\nWe care about your privacy.\nOpplysningen 1881 cannot see who calls you, who you call, or access your contacts in any way.\nRead more here: https://min.1881.no/vilkaar-personvern/personvernerklaring\n\nTerms of use\nhttps://min.1881.no/vilkaar-personvern/vilkar-1881-hvem-ringer","contentAdvisoryRating":"4+","averageUserRating":3.42857,"sellerUrl":"https://abonnement.1881.no/app","trackCensoredName":"1881 Who's Calling","languageCodesISO2A":["EN","NB"],"fileSizeBytes":"95655936","formattedPrice":"Free","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":14,"trackViewUrl":"https://apps.apple.com/no/app/1881-whos-calling/id593022780?uo=4","trackContentRating":"4+","averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":3.42857,"price":0.0,"artistId":593022783,"artistName":"Opplysningen 1881 AS","genres":["Reference","Utilities"],"userRatingCount":14}